2011-09-23T21:42:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/kotok-doubts-u-s-recession-says-stocks-at-entry-point-video.html
David Kotok , chairman and chief 
investment officer of Cumberland Advisors, talks about the 
outlook for the  U.S. economy  and his investment strategy.  Kotok also discusses U.S. stocks and Federal Reserve 
monetary policy. He speaks with  Matt Miller  and  Carol Massar  on 
Bloomberg Television's "Street Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:49
 